title: Grateful Dead Live at Saratoga Performing Arts Center on 1985-06-27
lineage: Master Cassette > Nakamichi CR7a playback with no dolby> Korg mr2000 (1 bit, 5.6 Mhz). Render from 1 bit to 24 48 wave file using AudioGate.  Pre dolby nr decode eq & software dolby B decode using Nuendo & DDICodec.
taper: Recorded & Transferred by Anon Edited & Mastered (Adobe Audition) by Joe Noel April 22, 2022
description:
Set I
In The Midnight Hour >
Bertha >
Little Red Rooster
Stagger Lee >
El Paso
Crazy Fingers >
Supplication >
High Time
Hell In A Bucket >
Don't Ease Me In
Set II
Feel Like A Stranger >
Eyes Of The World >
Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad >
Man Smart (Woman Smarter) >
Drums >
Space >
Truckin' >
Spoonful >
Black Peter >
Turn On Your Lovelight
Johnny B. Goode >
It's All Over Now Baby Blue

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
